00:42:00,199 --> 00:42:04,158
Boss! Toast more pancakes for me and pack them up.

582
00:42:04,158 --> 00:42:05,359
Please wait.

583
00:42:05,359 --> 00:42:07,418
- There're more, isn't it enough for you? 
  - Toast some more pancakes. 

584
00:42:07,418 --> 00:42:09,839
Well, Shiba didn't eat much just now.

585
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,300
I want to pack some for her, in case she's hungry.

586
00:42:19,780 --> 00:42:21,780
Check the bill!

587
00:42:21,780 --> 00:42:23,479
Coming.

588
00:42:30,199 --> 00:42:33,119
Young girl, you had a lot.

589
00:42:33,119 --> 00:42:34,799
Will you repudiate the bill?

590
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:36,999
Of course, I won't.

591
00:42:36,999 --> 00:42:38,419
But I was in a hurry.

592
00:42:38,419 --> 00:42:39,499
So I don't have enough money.

593
00:42:39,499 --> 00:42:41,980
Well, I can leave you a writing pledge.

594
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:43,980
I'll pay the rest of the money a few days later.

595
00:42:43,980 --> 00:42:45,338
What do you think?

596
00:42:45,338 --> 00:42:47,498
Young girl, are you kidding me?

597
00:42:47,498 --> 00:42:50,419
I'm doing a small business. You can't eat on credit.

598
00:42:50,419 --> 00:42:52,438
I think you should pay me the bill now.

599
00:42:52,439 --> 00:42:54,319
I said I would pay you later.

600
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:55,718
I won't repudiate the bill.

601
00:42:55,719 --> 00:42:58,279
I can give you twice as much, three times is also okay.

602
00:42:58,280 --> 00:43:01,038
Young girl, if you don't pay me the bill,

603
00:43:01,038 --> 00:43:04,739
I'll take you to our king now.

604
00:43:04,739 --> 00:43:07,600
Do you really think I have no money to pay you?

605
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:10,779
This is a handkerchief from the royal family of Central Plains.

606
00:43:10,779 --> 00:43:13,438
Its silk and the embroidery skills are perfect.

607
00:43:13,439 --> 00:43:16,839
This piece is at least worthy of five pearls.

608
00:43:16,839 --> 00:43:18,240
Five pearls.

609
00:43:18,240 --> 00:43:21,779
